To install the HTML Jargon File, do these steps:

1. Create a directory named `jargon' beneath your server's document root.

2. Copy all the HTML files in this distribution to this directory.

3. Edit the CGI file jargon-search to make $html_base correct.

4. Copy the CGI file jargon-search to your cgi-bin directory.

You're done.  Enjoy!
